

Role: Grant access to particular namespace.  it contains
 resources: what kinds of access fo which resources
 verbs: Action to list the resources,delete and watch the resources

ClusterRole: if you want ot provide access to complete cluster with all namespaces.The differnece between the role and clusterole is scope . it has complete access to cluster.
  

Role Binding and Cluster rolebinding

A role binding grants there permissions defined in a role to a user or set of users.it holds subject (usres,group,service accounts) ans permission being granted within a namespace is cal Rolebinding.

Clusterrolebinding: the rolebinding accross the cluster wide is clusterrolebinding.
